 813

 829        private Rect SubstractBorderPadding(Rect worldRect)
 0830        {
 831            // Case 1222517: We must take the scaling into consideration when applying local changes to the world rect.
 0832            float xScale = worldTransform.m00;
 0833            float yScale = worldTransform.m11;
 834
 0835            worldRect.x += resolvedStyle.borderLeftWidth * xScale;
 0836            worldRect.y += resolvedStyle.borderTopWidth * yScale;
 0837            worldRect.width -= (resolvedStyle.borderLeftWidth + resolvedStyle.borderRightWidth) * xScale;
 0838            worldRect.height -= (resolvedStyle.borderTopWidth + resolvedStyle.borderBottomWidth) * yScale;
 839
 0840            if (computedStyle.unityOverflowClipBox == OverflowClipBox.ContentBox)
 0841            {
 0842                worldRect.x += resolvedStyle.paddingLeft * xScale;
 0843                worldRect.y += resolvedStyle.paddingTop * yScale;
 0844                worldRect.width -= (resolvedStyle.paddingLeft + resolvedStyle.paddingRight) * xScale;
 0845                worldRect.height -= (resolvedStyle.paddingTop + resolvedStyle.paddingBottom) * yScale;
 0846            }
 847
 0848            return worldRect;
 0849        }

 851        // get the AA aligned bound
 852        internal static Rect ComputeAAAlignedBound(Rect position, Matrix4x4 mat)
 244853        {
 244854            Rect p = position;
 244855            Vector3 v0 = mat.MultiplyPoint3x4(new Vector3(p.x, p.y, 0.0f));
 244856            Vector3 v1 = mat.MultiplyPoint3x4(new Vector3(p.x + p.width, p.y, 0.0f));
 244857            Vector3 v2 = mat.MultiplyPoint3x4(new Vector3(p.x, p.y + p.height, 0.0f));
 244858            Vector3 v3 = mat.MultiplyPoint3x4(new Vector3(p.x + p.width, p.y + p.height, 0.0f));
 244859            return Rect.MinMaxRect(
 860                Mathf.Min(v0.x, Mathf.Min(v1.x, Mathf.Min(v2.x, v3.x))),
 861                Mathf.Min(v0.y, Mathf.Min(v1.y, Mathf.Min(v2.y, v3.y))),
 862                Mathf.Max(v0.x, Mathf.Max(v1.x, Mathf.Max(v2.x, v3.x))),
 863                Mathf.Max(v0.y, Mathf.Max(v1.y, Mathf.Max(v2.y, v3.y))));
 244864        }

 964            // by setting retargetRoot to retargetAgainst.m_PhysicalParent.
